==生平==
戴廷龍于2004年畢業於[[同濟大学|同濟大学]][[自動化|自動化]]系。2006年於[[香港科技大學|香港科技大學]]獲[[工業工程|工業工程]]及[[工業管理學系|工業管理學系]]（現名“工業工程及決策分析學系”）[[碩士|哲學碩士]]學位<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.ielm.ust.hk/eng/event_detail.php?type=S&id=333 | title=Join IE/OM Seminar Incentive Contracting With Operational Considerations | date=June 2016 | accessdate=September 8, 2016 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111161320/https://www.ielm.ust.hk/eng/event_detail.php?type=S&id=333 | archive-date=2017-01-11 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。 2007年至2013年期間師從{{Link-en|史泰佑|Sridhar Tayur}}及{{Link-en|斯凱洛|Katia Sycara}}，获[[卡內基梅隆大學|卡內基梅隆大學]][[商學院|商學院]]及{{Link-en|機器人研究所|Robotics Institute}}聯合授予[[哲學博士|哲學博士]]学位。2013年起，獲聘為[[約翰·霍普金斯大學|約翰·霍普金斯大學]]<ref name="jh-dai">{{cite web | url=http://carey.jhu.edu/faculty-research/faculty-directory/tinglong-dai-phd | title=Tinglong Dai, PhD, Johns Hopkins | publisher=carey.jhu.edu | date=June 2013 | accessdate=September 8, 2016 | archive-date=2018-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712024228/https://carey.jhu.edu/faculty-research/faculty-directory/tinglong-dai-phd | dead-url=no }}</ref>助理教授，之後於2018年晉升為副教授。2021年起戴廷龍成為終身正教授。商業教育網站''Poets & Quants''將他評為世界最佳 40 位 40 歲以下商學院教授<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Allen|first=Nathan|date=2021-05-03|title=Poets&Quants {{!}} Poets&Quants' Best 40-Under-40 Business School Professors Of 2021|url=https://poetsandquants.com/2021/05/03/poetsquants-best-40-under-40-business-school-professors-of-2021/|access-date=2021-09-05|website=Poets&Quants|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210905023021/https://poetsandquants.com/2021/05/03/poetsquants-best-40-under-40-business-school-professors-of-2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Allen|first=Nathan|date=2021-05-03|title=Poets&Quants {{!}} 2021 Best 40-Under-40 Professors: Tinglong Dai, Johns Hopkins University (Carey)|url=https://poetsandquants.com/2021/05/03/2021-best-40-under-40-professors-tinglong-dai-johns-hopkins-university-carey/?pq-category=best-profs|access-date=2021-09-05|website=Poets&Quants|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210905023020/https://poetsandquants.com/2021/05/03/2021-best-40-under-40-professors-tinglong-dai-johns-hopkins-university-carey/?pq-category=best-profs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

戴廷龍于2012年获{{Link-en|美國運營管理學會 (POMS)|Operations_management#Organizations}}最佳醫療管理論文獎<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.poms.org/POMS%20Chronicle%20Vol%2019%20No%201.pdf | title=Healthcare Operations Management Best Paper Award | newspaper=POMS Chronicle | date=2012 | accessdate=September 8, 2016 | volume=19 | number=1 | archive-date=2020-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125135632/http://www.poms.org/POMS%20Chronicle%20Vol%2019%20No%201.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2012年獲{{Link-en|國際運籌學與管理科學學會 (INFORMS)|Institute for Operations Research and the Management Sciences}}皮尔斯卡拉獎(Pierskalla Award)第二名<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.informs.org/Recognize-Excellence/Community-Prizes-and-Awards/Health-Applications-Society/Pierskalla-Best-Paper-Award | title=Pierskalla Best Paper Award | date=October 2012 | accessdate=September 8, 2016 | publisher=INFORMS | website=informs.org | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513203612/https://www.informs.org/Recognize-Excellence/Community-Prizes-and-Awards/Health-Applications-Society/Pierskalla-Best-Paper-Award | archivedate=2016年5月13日 }}</ref>。 他于2015年及2020年兩度以[[精準醫學|精準醫學]]相關的[[跨学科|跨学科研究]]獲[[約翰·霍普金斯大學|約翰·霍普金斯大學]]'''發現獎'''(The Johns Hopkins Discovery Award)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.jhu.edu/administration/provost/awards/Discovery_Award/discovery |work=Johns Hopkins University Office of the Provost |date=2015 |accessdate=September 8, 2016 |title=Johns Hopkins Discovery Award |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030185406/http://web.jhu.edu/administration/provost/awards/Discovery_Award/discovery |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news  | url=http://www.jhunewsletter.com/2015/09/17/university-creates-young-faculty-awards/  | title=University creates young faculty awards  | newspaper=The Johns Hopkins News-Letter  | date=September 17, 2015  | accessdate=September 8, 2016  | author=Marcia Zimmerman  | archive-date=2017-01-11  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111161222/http://www.jhunewsletter.com/2015/09/17/university-creates-young-faculty-awards/  | dead-url=no  }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=JHU Honors Three on Carey Faculty|url=https://carey.jhu.edu/articles/jhu-honors-three-carey-faculty|access-date=2021-09-05|website=carey.jhu.edu|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210905192949/https://carey.jhu.edu/articles/jhu-honors-three-carey-faculty|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年戴廷龍獲國際運籌學與管理科學學會 (INFORMS)公共部門最佳論文獎<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.informs.org/Recognizing-Excellence/Community-Prizes/Public-Sector-O.R/Public-Sector-OR-Best-Paper-Competition|title=Public Sector OR Best Paper Competition|accessdate=2018-07-11|author=|date=|last=|work=|publisher=Institute for Operations Research and the Management Sciences|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711202413/https://www.informs.org/Recognizing-Excellence/Community-Prizes/Public-Sector-O.R/Public-Sector-OR-Best-Paper-Competition|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

